com.i2group.apollo.security

Class WebSphereRoleBasedPrincipalProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.security.WebSphereRoleBasedPrincipalProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPrincipalProvider

    public class WebSphereRoleBasedPrincipalProvider
extends Object
implements IPrincipalProvider
    A WebSphere-specific implementation of IPrincipalProvider that maps the roles of the Principal to values in the available access and grant SecurityDimensions.

    This implementation requires that no two SecurityDimensions of the same type (access or grant) have values with the same names.

    Since:
    4.0
